Use the circle pad to steer
Hold the L or R button while turning to move left or right quickly
Press the L or R button twice to do a barrel roll. It repels enemy fire.
Press the Y button to launch a bomb. Press the Y button again to detonate it
Press the A button to fire your laser. Hold the A button if you want to charge it
You can also lock on to enemies when charging your laser
When locked on to an enemy, you can even launch bombs
If you destroy multiple enemies at once, you'll earn bonus points
Collecting a silver ring will refill some of your shield gauge
Collecting three gold rings will increase your shield gauge
Collecting a laser item will power up your laser
Hyper lasers are more powerful than twins
Collecting a wing repair item will fix your wings
Press the X button to boost
Press the B button to brake
To do a somersault, slide the circle pad down and boost at the same time
You can do U Turns in All Range Mode
To do a U Turn, slide the circle pad down and brake at the same time
Remember, U Turns only work in All Range Mode
Press right on the plus control pad to change your point of view

Hold it longer for greater effect

Collect three more for an extra arwing

To ascend, slide the circle pad down, to descend, slide the circle pad up.
Press the B button to fire your laser. Hold the B button to charge it
Press the A button to brake
